    dc:description "FIGURES 43 – 48. Scirtothrips araucariae sp. n. (43) Head and pronotum; (44) Antennal segments II – VIII; (45) Tergites IV – VI; (46) Sternites V – VII; (47) Mesonotum and metanotum; (48) Tergites VII – IX." ;
